{"tid":428964,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人越大個人越易攰","createTime":"2017-10-08T13:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T06:24:27.000Z","uid":143474,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e37c55d19bffd0ec47f08a6f89581e1cfef8d1f2","tid":428964,"uid":143474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:07:49.000Z","msg":"諗返起year 1 / 2個陣可以通頂溫書直落考試<br />\n又可以唔訓同friend 吹水飲酒打牌到天光再上九半堂<br />\n<br />\n去到而家year 4 一到十二點幾一點就好眼訓<br />\n訓七八個鐘都好攰，一放假就唔想去玩，只係想訓教<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db566607682a813eaf9e7d7a6bc92982824710e9","tid":428964,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:09:59.000Z","msg":"老了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f749e43bc7ab6021661a02d68a3f3dddffaa6d","tid":428964,"uid":82764,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:10:33.000Z","msg":"正常人都係咁<br />\n完"},{"pid":"8d7b5ec85553c3e931f207489c2dde52ca951f70","tid":428964,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:11:11.000Z","msg":"攰緊﹐上個星期打完波到依家都仲攰緊"},{"pid":"50c6794e453770f04024be580b2c390a938bdb8f","tid":428964,"uid":143474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:26:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>攰緊﹐上個星期打完波到依家都仲攰緊</blockquote><br />\n明明今日放假無咩點做野都攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe9d789c24b2de1fd150cbbffd201ca14f541a8","tid":428964,"uid":76941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:34:41.000Z","msg":"Year 1-4都可以通頂溫書趕功課直落<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家一放工掂到張床已經想訓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3c4d0ee3afac02706da4b10f920f77a2521571","tid":428964,"uid":151619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>攰緊﹐上個星期打完波到依家都仲攰緊</blockquote><br />\n明明今日放假無咩點做野都攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以全日係屋企都攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96c9a0a352b41c8aae07f172c93437b785bb081","tid":428964,"uid":72608,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:44:10.000Z","msg":"老係一個因素<br />\n<br />\n但主要都係因為你既生活習慣唔健康,唔夠養生,時間積累..所以先易攰"},{"pid":"d139421a846fe0bffb5bc38ec26fc503ebfc61b0","tid":428964,"uid":63649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  依家愈嚟愈注意養生 人愈忙愈在意假期 一個星期得一日抖 又要讀書又要搵錢為將來 連出去飲酒行到老遠食餐好都懶"},{"pid":"4c0561be1a2af87837790c87ca8a7f4eb77a5292","tid":428964,"uid":13518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T13:49:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Year 1-4都可以通頂溫書趕功課直落<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家一放工掂到張床已經想訓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係點解？真係一返full part就開始攰<br />\n心攰身攰同開始殘<br />\n我搵左一年前自己返part time既相同而家返full time既相做左個比較<br />\n一年前個樣係細個好多皮膚好好多唔殘精靈<br />\n一年後望到自己真係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f21b148c63679282cd3a2d5d805c512f190648","tid":428964,"uid":150611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T14:11:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb3d30342319ba69cdd05c6155a508932478abeb","tid":428964,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T14:12:49.000Z","msg":"人生冇意義了"},{"pid":"b001863ccbd949d6b5a8ed0847be9dc3110c395f","tid":428964,"uid":76941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T14:15:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Year 1-4都可以通頂溫書趕功課直落<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家一放工掂到張床已經想訓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係點解？真係一返full part就開始攰<br />\n心攰身攰同開始殘<br />\n我搵左一年前自己返part time既相同而家返full time既相做左個比較<br />\n一年前個樣係細個好多皮膚好好多唔殘精靈<br />\n一年後望到自己真係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為讀書果陣壓力真係冇咁大<br />\n出黎做野之後要顧既野多左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 一直full time 做野 part time讀書<br />\n但讀緊書果陣唔知點解真係精神好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53feedc00f41d224d33454454cf21e7edd0424c","tid":428964,"uid":152080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T14:16:32.000Z","msg":"睇得愈透愈頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed53a8bd1797855b048fe69df5541c6399c51716","tid":428964,"uid":38122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T14:19:29.000Z","msg":"做左近十年野<br />\n由以前打機打到2am訓 <br />\n到而家無興趣打 11pm左右就訓<br />\n出到黎做野仲攰"},{"pid":"ce4186195e4fcc20cd2656375330d16681d63ea0","tid":428964,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做左近十年野<br />\n由以前打機打到2am訓 <br />\n到而家無興趣打 11pm左右就訓<br />\n出到黎做野仲攰</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hk has no work-life balance"},{"pid":"096b208589bc78603a30b9620fcc904ed1539b33","tid":428964,"uid":11258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T14:32:14.000Z","msg":"老啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1643da77c34fc416f06d52b16c4f71b00dd6d2b1","tid":428964,"uid":112873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T14:33:49.000Z","msg":"打丁打太多啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"